title: Giant dipole resonance on Ni isotopes.

x4freetext: Giant dipole resonance on Ni isotopes.

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Soviet Journal of Nuclear Physics, Vol.11, p.141 (1970)

x4freetext: Photoneutron production  cross   sections   for   two
isotopes, 58Ni and 60Ni,  are obtained in the region
of the giant dipole resonance. They have complicated
structures and  large  widths.  The  integral  cross
section up to 30 MeV is 310 MeV*mb for 58Ni and  620
MeV*mb for 60Ni. Total absorption cross sections for
